  stimulus_text = 'The author’s use of the word "writhing" is significant because it suggests the character is experiencing a great deal of physical and emotional pain. The reader understands the character’s suffering through this vivid imagery. What is the effect of the author’s use of the word "writhing"? Researchers note that the pattern described above remained consistent across repeated observations, suggesting the finding was not a one-time anomaly. They caution that local conditions can still vary, yet the overall relationship held in each documented case.',
